name: OpenFloorPlan
tagline: Web Tools for Creating and Interacting with Building Floorplans
body:
### Welcome to OpenFloorPlan

OpenFloorPlan is a set of open source JavaScript libraries that can be used to manipulate and interact with SVG-based floor plans in HTML5 or NodeJS.

For more information please see https://github.com/openfloorplan

### Contact
Email: info@openfloorplan.org
or contact Kris Carle (@kriscarle) on GitHub.

### By SYNCADD Systems

OpenFloorPlan is an open source development project by SYNCADD http://www.syncadd.com
